doctype html 
html  
  head
    title= title
    link(href= "css/urlShortener.css", rel = "stylesheet")
  body
      h3.msg= msg
      h1.main FreeCodeCamp API Basejump: URL Shortener Microservice
      
      
      h3 Use cases:
      div.stories 
        p 1) You can pass a URL as a parameter and it will check to see whether that string contains a valid URL
        p 2) If it does, it returns a changed url which is shorter than original
        p 3) If it does not contain a valid URL, it returns error.
        p Be Careful about putting /new after base-url before adding your url.
      
      div.examples 
        h3 Example usage:
        p https://fccshortener-nishant-tomer.c9users.io/urlshortener/new/https://www.google.com
        p https://fccshortener-nishant-tomer.c9users.io/urlshortener/new/http://foo.com:80
      
      div.output
        h3 Example output:
        p { "original_url":"http://foo.com:80", "short_url":"https://fccshortener-nishant-tomer.c9users.io/us/8170" }